     C           #CHK30    BEGSR
     C*
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    W3SHIN
     C                     MOVE F3KNBN    WWKNBN
     C                     SETOF                     9961
     C*
     C                     DO
     C*
     C           F3KNBN    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     SETON                     9961
